OL,7,FSince ITV News aired Fiona's story and
OL,8,Fthe prime minister's subsequent pledge
OL,9,Fin the Commons to "look into" the law
OL,10,Fchange, we have been contacted by
OL,11,Fother families who are also battling
OL,12,Fto get mental capacity assessments.
OL,14,FOne father told of the "horrific"
OL,15,Fexperience he had trying to help his
OL,16,Fautistic daughter out of a coercive
OL,17,Fand controlling relationship with a
OL,18,Fman, who exploited her and "drained"
OL,19,Fher finances.
