OL,7,F"We'll continue that engagement
OL,8,Fthroughout the passage of the bill and
OL,9,Fsee if there is a workable way in
OL,10,Fwhich we can improve this bill to make
OL,11,Fsure that others do not have to go
OL,12,Fthrough the unimaginable heartbreak
OL,13,Fthat Fiona is living with every day."
OL,15,FThe health secretary also thanked the
