OL,14,Fson - as well as his speech on Monday
OL,15,Fnight.
OL,17,FHe told MPs as he urged them to back
OL,18,Fthe law change: "Although this
OL,19,Famendment is only a small part of the
OL,20,Fanswer, it is an answer to save lives.
